com.vmware.nsx_policy.aaa

Class AaaFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.aaa.AaaFactory

  • public class AaaFactory
extends Object
    AaaFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.aaa package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
